# VyaparAI Project Setup Instructions

Welcome! Follow these steps to run the project on your machine.

## 1. Clone the repository

Open your terminal and run:

bash
git clone https://github.com/Namratathale/VyaparAI.git
cd your-repo

cd vyapar-ai
npm install
npm start

2. 
cd vyapar-server
npm install
npm start

3. Access the application
Frontend usually runs on http://localhost:3000
Backend usually runs on http://localhost:5000
 (adjust if different)
4. Pull updates

To update your local copy with the latest changes, run:

git pull origin main


